SUMMER VENGEANCE MATCH
SARAH JANE
Blondie
HT: 5'6
WT: 109lbs
Lifetime record (1-6)
Ranked 15th
ANNIE CRUZ
The Scorpion
HT: 5'6
WT: 118lbs
Lifetime record (1-6)
Ranked 16th
Welcome to the second annual Summer Vengeance elimination tournament. The top sixteen Season Five wrestlers battle it out to see who will be the overall Ultimate Surrender champion for 2008.
We have two girls with identical stats, height and weight. Both have 7 matches, both have only one win, both wins against the same opponent.
Who wants it more? Who wants to go on to the next round? One girl will advance, one girl will go home - her season ending today.
Join today and get in on the ground floor of the 2008 Championship Tournament that will end with one overall Champion!
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE BEGINS!
